# Order System (Java)

## Overview
A simple order system implemented in Java demonstrating:

- Object-Oriented Design
- Strategy Pattern (Payment)
- Factory Pattern

## Features
- Create orders
- Add products
- Calculate total price
- Pay with different strategies

## Run

```bash
javac -d out src/main/java/edu/orderSys/**/*.java
java -cp out edu/orderSys.MainApp

Design Patterns
Strategy Pattern
Factory Pattern